law.history: Repealed 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 512, sec. 15, effective July 13, 1990. -- Amended 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 2, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1986. -- Amended 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 393, sec. 33, effective July 15, 1982. -- Created 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 231, sec. 2, effective June 17, 1978.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Request for space by agency -- Determination of need by department for facilities management -- Advertisement for leasing proposals -- Award of lease by commissioner -- Limited judicial review -- Report to capital projects and bond committee.
